content: प्रणीत {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} {@--1@} Put forward, advanced, presented. {@--2@} Delivered, given, offered, presented. {@--3@} Brought into, reduced to. {@--4@} Executed, effected, performed. {@--5@} Taught, prescribed. {@--6@} Cast, sent, discharged. {@--7@} Brought to, set. {@--8@} Written, composed. {@--9@} Set aside, removed. {@--10@} Agreeable or pleasing. {@--11@} Inflicted (as punishment); see प्रणी above. --तः Fire consecrated by prayers. --ता A sacrificed vessel. --तं Anything cooked or dressed, such as a condiment.
